TITLE "Permian band-validation: recombination saturated locus up to p_c + EOS critical point"

; Same EOS as the GOR2000 deck (Milan's Permian model). OILREF/GASREF are the
; equilibrium phases of GOR2000 flashed at 2000 psia / 200 F;
; recombined to a spread of saturation pressures running oil-like -> near-critical
; to trace the saturated locus up toward the critical point (the supercritical band).
; Generated by scripts/gen_phazecomp_band_validation.py -- edit the generator, not this file.

STAB  ON

INCLUDE eos.inc
INCLUDE compositions.inc

; ---- reference split: flash GOR2000 at 2000 psia / 200 F (two-phase) ----
MIX FEED GOR2000 1 MOLE
TEMP 200 F
PRES 2000 PSIA
FLASH
MIX OILREF EQL 1 MOLE
MIX GASREF EQV 1 MOLE

; ---- recombined sibling fluids (mole basis: <amt> MOLE <src>) ----
MIX SIB150 0.85 MOLE OILREF 0.15 MOLE GASREF
MIX SIB250 0.75 MOLE OILREF 0.25 MOLE GASREF
MIX SIB350 0.65 MOLE OILREF 0.35 MOLE GASREF
MIX SIB450 0.55 MOLE OILREF 0.45 MOLE GASREF
MIX SIB520 0.48 MOLE OILREF 0.52 MOLE GASREF
MIX SIB580 0.42 MOLE OILREF 0.58 MOLE GASREF
MIX SIB620 0.38 MOLE OILREF 0.62 MOLE GASREF
MIX SIB660 0.34 MOLE OILREF 0.66 MOLE GASREF
MIX SIB700 0.30 MOLE OILREF 0.70 MOLE GASREF
MIX SIB740 0.26 MOLE OILREF 0.74 MOLE GASREF

; ============== SATURATED LOCUS (psat + locus flash per sibling) ==============

; ----- sibling OILREF (GASREF fraction 0.00) -----

NOTE: "===SATP=== FLUID=OILREF  T=200 F  (upper saturation pressure)"
MIX FEED OILREF 1 MOLE
TEMP 200 F
SATP

NOTE: "===FLASHPOINT=== FLUID=OILREF P=1996.00 PSIA  T=200 F  (LOCUS)"
MIX FEED OILREF 1 MOLE
TEMP 200 F
PRES 1996.00 PSIA
FLASH
MIX FEED EQL 1 MOLE
DLE ID "OIL SEP FLUID=OILREF P=1996.00 PSIA: 100/60F | 14.696/60F -> Rs=CumGOR, Bo=1/LiqVol"
BASIS 1 BBL
STAGE               TEMP                PRES                GOR                 CUMGOR              LVOL         K-C1
                    F                   PSIA                SCF/BBL             SCF/BBL             BBL
1                   60                  100
2                   60                  14.696
END
MIX FEED OILREF 1 MOLE
TEMP 200 F
PRES 1996.00 PSIA
FLASH
MIX FEED EQV 1 MOLE
DLE ID "GAS SEP FLUID=OILREF P=1996.00 PSIA: 100/60F | 14.696/60F -> rs=1e6/CumGOR"
BASIS 1 BBL
STAGE               TEMP                PRES                GOR                 CUMGOR              LVOL         K-C1
                    F                   PSIA                SCF/BBL             SCF/BBL             BBL
1                   60                  100
2                   60                  14.696
END

